{"id":670512,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/670512.html","date":"2021-09-07T03:03:11Z","modified":"2021-09-07T07:45:13Z","title":"【404帖子】简中赛博坟场｜因发表“西安地铁保安拖曳女乘客”相关内容，大量博主遭删帖禁言","content":"<p>编者按：本文内容大多数来自电报频道<a href=\"https://t.me/cybergraveyardcn/796\" title=\"简中赛博坟场\">简中赛博坟场</a>的收集和记录。</p>\n<p>2021年8月30日，西安地铁3号线上一位女乘客因与其他乘客发生口角，被安保人员暴力拖曳下车，在撕扯中衣不蔽体，其现场视频在网络上激起了公愤，舆论要求西安地铁道歉并承担责任，之后，相关信息在各个社媒平台上不断被审查。</p>\n<p>网传一位女孩因在地铁举牌抗议而被警察带走：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/09/image-1630997122195.png\" alt=\"imgv\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/09/image-1630997060317.png\" alt=\"imgv\" /></p>\n<p>网传西安地铁事件的女当事人遭到辞退：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/09/IMG_0573-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"cdtimg\" /></p>\n<p>微博管理员发布公告，指数千个账号因“非理性”评论西安地铁保安拖拽女乘客事件，遭到禁言和炸号：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/09/西安地铁炸号.png\" alt=\"cdtimg\" /></p>\n<p>微博博主@芋次郎 为西安地铁事件中女当事人以及抗议者发声，微博被炸并被喝茶。相关豆瓣讨论被删除：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/09/IMG_0575.jpg\" alt=\"cdtimg\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/09/IMG_0576.jpg\" alt=\"cdtimg\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/09/IMG_0577.jpg\" alt=\"cdtimg\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/09/IMG_0578.jpg\" alt=\"cdtimg\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/09/IMG_0579.jpg\" alt=\"cdtimg\" /></p>\n<p>网传西安政府在组织公职人员举报西安地铁事件网络负面信息：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/09/IMG_0547-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"cdtimg\" /></p>\n<p>微博话题#西安地铁回应女乘客被保安拖曳#被禁止搜索：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/09/IMG_0581.jpg\" alt=\"cdtimg\" /></p>\n<p>微博用户@雾港水手 表达与受害女性的共情，其微博被删后被禁言90天：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/09/IMG_0582.jpg\" alt=\"cdtimg\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/09/IMG_0583.jpg\" alt=\"cdtimg\" /></p>\n<p>微博用户@暴烈甜心小鳄鱼毛毛 针对西安地铁事件提起公诉请求书，转发量达6.2万，其微博被删除，账号被禁言：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/09/IMG_0585.jpg\" alt=\"cdtimg\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/09/IMG_0586.jpg\" alt=\"cdtimg\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/09/IMG_0587.jpg\" alt=\"cdtimg\" /></p>\n<p>微博话题#西安警方介于地铁女乘客被拖离事件#被禁止搜索：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/09/IMG_0588.jpg\" alt=\"cdtimg\" /></p>\n<p>西安地铁举牌抗议相关图片被屏蔽，相关微博疑被删除，发布者被禁言：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/09/IMG_0589.jpg\" alt=\"cdtimg\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/09/IMG_0590.jpg\" alt=\"cdtimg\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/09/IMG_0591.jpg\" alt=\"cdtimg\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/09/IMG_0592.jpg\" alt=\"cdtimg\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/09/IMG_0593.jpg\" alt=\"cdtimg\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/09/IMG_0594.jpg\" alt=\"cdtimg\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/09/IMG_0595.jpg\" alt=\"cdtimg\" /></p>\n<p>微博用户@一畔孤鸿 因转发西安地铁事件相关微博被禁言：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/09/IMG_0546.jpg\" alt=\"cdtimg\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/09/IMG_0545.jpg\" alt=\"cdtimg\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/09/IMG_0544.jpg\" alt=\"cdtimg\" /></p>\n<p>西安地铁举牌相关微博被删除：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/09/IMG_0543.jpg\" alt=\"cdtimg\" /></p>\n","author":1067,"categories":[41492,38912,38917,15868,18271],"tags":[20562,43834,10367,44112,14804]}